# Hin th y  bng vi thanh trt ngang
pd.set_option('display.max_columns', None)   

# To colormap trng  xanh lc
custom_green = LinearSegmentedColormap.from_list("custom_green", ["#ffffff", "#00cc66"])

# Hnm t mu
def highlight_warning_full(row):
    styles = [""] * len(row)
    col_idx = row.index.tolist()

    # Index cc ct
    idx_y = col_idx.index("y true") if "y true" in col_idx else None
    idx_set = col_idx.index("Prediction Set") if "Prediction Set" in col_idx else None
    idx_correct = col_idx.index("Correct in set") if "Correct in set" in col_idx else None
    idx_size = col_idx.index("Set size") if "Set size" in col_idx else None

    # iu kin t mu chnh
    if idx_y is not None and idx_set is not None and idx_correct is not None:
        if not row["Correct in set"]:
            color = "background-color: #f8696b; color: black; font-weight: bold"  # 
        elif row["Set size"] == 1:
            color = "background-color: #00cc66; color: black; font-weight: bold"  # xanh lc
        else:
            color = "background-color: yellow; color: black; font-weight: bold"  # vng

        styles[idx_y] = color
        styles[idx_set] = color
        styles[idx_correct] = color

    # Ct Set size
    if idx_size is not None:
        if row["Set size"] == 1:
            styles[idx_size] = "background-color: white; color: black; font-weight: bold"
        else:
            styles[idx_size] = "background-color: #b590ff; color: black; font-weight: bold"

    return styles

# Cc t l thun nghch ch  lm cho d liu gn vi thc t hn trnh Mu thun c bn, tuy nhin cn to NHIU cho mi bin  to Sai s thc t ngc li (to Mu thun nh hn to s ngu nhin)
# 1. position:           cn chia lm 5 gi tr, tuy nhin cp  rt quan trng v n nh hng n cc bin khc
# 2. contracts_signed:   cc cp cng cao nh Senior hay Manager th k kt trung bnh; junior cn t nht cn  gia l mid level v associates th nhiu nht, ni chung l gn ging phn phi chun tuy nhin trong gia cc nhn vin ca cng 1 lp th trong  li c phn phi chun ngu nhin na
# 3. transaction_value:  t l thun vi contracts_signed v thun mnh vi positions
# 4. customers_served:   t l lm sao  cc cp position cng cao th customer_served cng thp nhng contracts_signed cng cao
# 5. kpi_completion:     to mt ct transaction_target (ct ph, khng a vo dataframe)  tnh kpi_completion cp cng cao th transaction_target cng phi cao hn cp thp)
# 6. nps_score:          t l thun mt cht vi contracts_signed
# 7. customer_rating:    ty 
# 8. feedback_score:     ty  
# 9. transaction_time:   t l nghch mt cht vi customer_rating
# 10. task_per_day:      t l vi cp position
# 11. error_rate:        t l thun mt cht vi task_per_day (cng lm nhiu cng d sai st)
# 12. experience_years:  t l thun mt cht vi cp  position
# 13. work_hours_weekly: t l thun mt cht vi cp  position
# 14. training_courses:  t l thun hi mnh vi experience_years
# 15. certifications:    ty

# S lng nhn vin (s quan st)
n = 100000

# Gi kt qu khi chy li
np.random.seed(42) 

## 0. ID nhn vin (ct ny  kim tra nu cn, khng ng gp vo m hnh)
employee_ids = [f"{str(i).zfill(4)}" for i in range(1, n + 1)]

###### CH  CHN PHN PHI PH HP VI THC T THEO TNG BIN U VO ######
## 1. position: V tr - chc v
position = np.random.choice(['Nhn vin', 'Chuyn vin', 'Trng nhm', 'Qun l'], size=n, p=[0.5, 0.35, 0.1, 0.05])
pos_to_numeric = {'Nhn vin': 1, 'Chuyn vin': 2, 'Trng nhm': 3, 'Qun l': 4} # Chuyn thnh s 
pos_numeric = np.array([pos_to_numeric[p] for p in position]) - 1  # Chuyn thnh s  sau ny tnh cc bin c tng quan

## 2. contracts_signed: S hp ng  k
contracts_mean = [6, 12, 8, 3]  # Trung bnh hp ng k theo cp bc   
contracts_signed = np.round(np.random.lognormal(mean=np.log(np.take(contracts_mean, pos_numeric)), sigma=0.3, size=n))

## 3. transaction_value: Gi tr/Khi lng giao dch
transaction_mean = [20, 50, 150, 500]  # Gi tr giao dch trung bnh theo cp bc  
transaction_value = np.round(contracts_signed * np.random.lognormal(mean=np.log(np.take(transaction_mean, pos_numeric)), sigma=0.4, size=n), 2)

## 4. customers_served: S khch hng  phc v/giao dch
customers_mean = [50, 80, 20, 10]  # S khch hng trung bnh theo cp bc  
customers_served = np.round(np.random.gamma(shape=np.take(customers_mean, pos_numeric) / 2, scale=2, size=n))

## 5. kpi_completion: T l hon thnh ch tiu doanh s
transaction_target_base = [20, 50, 150, 500]  # Ch tiu giao dch theo cp (Ct ph c n i trnh a cng tuyn vi ct KPI chnh)
transaction_target = np.take(transaction_target_base, pos_numeric) * contracts_signed # Gn ch tiu cho cc cp 
multiplier_target = np.random.normal(loc=1.0, scale=0.1, size=n) # Thm nhiu cho ging thc t
transaction_target = np.round(transaction_target * multiplier_target, 2)
kpi_completion = np.round((transaction_value / transaction_target) * 100, 2) 

## 6. NPS_Score: Net Prommote Score 
nps_mean = [20, 30, 40, 50] # NPS trung bnh theo cp
nps_base = np.take(nps_mean, pos_numeric) 
contracts_mean_overall = np.mean(contracts_signed)
nps_adjustment = 0.5 * (contracts_signed - contracts_mean_overall) # Gi s s hp ng nh hng ti im trung bnh NPS 0.5 im
nps_mean_adjusted = nps_base + nps_adjustment # iu chnh NPS theo hiu sut k hp ng
nps_score = np.round(np.random.normal(loc=nps_mean_adjusted, scale=8, size=n), 2) # Thm nhiu
nps_score = np.clip(nps_score, -20, 60) # Gii hn

## 7. customer_rating: nh gi khch hng 1-5 sao
customer_rating = np.round(3.5 + 1.5 * np.random.beta(4, 2, n), 1)

## 8. feedback_score: nh gi 360 t ng nghip
feedback_score = np.round((np.clip(np.random.normal(8, 1.2, n), 4, 10) +           # Phn hi t Cp cao
                          np.clip(np.random.normal(9, 1.5, n), 4, 10)) / 2, 1)     # Phn hi t cp ngang v thp hn

## 9. transaction_time: Thi gian trung bnh x l mt 1 giao dch
transaction_time = np.round(np.clip(30 / customer_rating * np.random.lognormal(0, 0.4, n), 5, 60), 2)

## 10. task_per_day: S yu cu x l/giao dch/vic phi lm mi ngy
task_per_day = np.random.poisson(lam=12, size=n)

## 11. error_rate: T l li trong cng vic
error_rate = np.round(np.clip(np.random.beta(2, 5, n) * 0.1 * task_per_day, 0, 1.2), 2)

## 12. experience_years: S nm kinh nghim lm vic
experience_mean = [3, 7, 8, 15] # Trung bnh nm kinh nghim cho tng v tr
experience_std = [1, 2.5, 3, 5] # Thm nhiu cho tng v tr cho thc t
experience_years = np.round([np.clip(np.random.normal(loc=experience_mean[i], scale=experience_std[i]), 0, None) for i in pos_numeric], 1)

## 13. work_hours_per_week: S gi lm vic mi tun
base_work_hours = [48, 50, 55, 60]  # Gi lm vic trung bnh theo v tr
work_hours_per_week = np.round(np.clip(np.random.normal([base_work_hours[i] for i in pos_numeric], 5), 30, 70), 1)

## 14. training_courses: S kha hc  c o to
trained_courses = np.round(np.clip(np.random.normal(3 + experience_years * 0.2, 1), 0, 10), 0)

## 15. certifications: S chng ch 
certifications = np.random.poisson(lam=2, size=n)  

# To DataFrame (16 ct bao gm 1 ct ID, 15 ct c trng)
df = pd.DataFrame({
    "Employee_ID": employee_ids,
    "Position": position,
    "Contracts_Signed": contracts_signed,
    "Transaction_Value": transaction_value,
    "Customers_Served": customers_served,
    "KPI_Completion_%": kpi_completion,
    "NPS_Score": nps_score,
    "Customer_Rating": customer_rating,
    "Feedback_Score": feedback_score,
    "Transaction_Time_Min": transaction_time,
    "Tasks_Per_Day": task_per_day,
    "Error_Rate_%": error_rate,
    "Experience_Years": experience_years,
    "Work_Hours_Weekly": work_hours_per_week,
    "Trained_Courses": trained_courses,
    "Certifications": certifications
})

# Hm chun ha min-max
def normalize_min_max(series):
    return (series - series.min()) / (series.max() - series.min())

# Hm chun ha o ngc (cng thp cng tt)
def normalize_inverse_min_max(series):
    return 1 - ((series - series.min()) / (series.max() - series.min()))

# Chun ha cc ct cn thit
df['contracts_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['Contracts_Signed'])
df['transaction_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['Transaction_Value'])
df['KPI_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['KPI_Completion_%'])
df['NPS_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['NPS_Score'])
df['Customer_Rating_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['Customer_Rating'])
df['Feedback_norm'] = normalize_min_max(df['Feedback_Score'])

# Chun ha o ngc cho cc ct "cng thp cng tt"
df['Transaction_Time_Inv'] = normalize_inverse_min_max(df['Transaction_Time_Min'])
df['Error_Rate_Inv'] = normalize_inverse_min_max(df['Error_Rate_%'])

# nh ngha trng s cho tng ch s (tng = 1)
weights = {
    'contracts': 0.05,
    'transactions': 0.05,
    'KPI': 0.5,               
    'NPS': 0.1,               
    'Customer_Rating': 0.05,   
    'Feedback': 0.05,          
    'Transaction_Time': 0.05, 
    'Error_Rate': 0.05       
}

# Tnh im tng hp
df['Composite_Score'] = (
    df['contracts_norm'] * weights['contracts'] +
    df['transaction_norm'] * weights['transactions'] +
    df['KPI_norm'] * weights['KPI'] +
    df['NPS_norm'] * weights['NPS'] +
    df['Customer_Rating_norm'] * weights['Customer_Rating'] +
    df['Feedback_norm'] * weights['Feedback'] +
    df['Transaction_Time_Inv'] * weights['Transaction_Time'] +
    df['Error_Rate_Inv'] * weights['Error_Rate']
)
  • SETTING PHN PHI Y, THAY I CC MC CT THRESHOLD THAY I S LNG CHO C 4 NHN

# Xc nh ngng phn loi
rating_bins = [-np.inf, 0.23, 0.29, 0.36, np.inf]  # Tng ng vi Km, Trung Bnh, Tt, Xut Sc

# Phn loi nhn vin

    df['Composite_Score'],
    bins=rating_bins,
    labels=rating_labels,
    right=False  
)

2. M HNH PHN LOI

2.1: LU V TRAIN TEST SPLIT (QUAN TRNG)

  • PIPELINE KHI S DNG MAPIE
    • Mapie Clf phn 3 cn s dng thm 1 tp X/y_Cal, vit tt ca Calibration, s gii thch bc 3 sau.
    • Tm thi ch cn nh: thay v chia thnh 2 tp Train/Test - 70/30, 75/25, 80/20, ... nh mi khi th ta cn chia thm tp Cal nh na
  • CCH CHIA
    • T l: chia 2 ln, chia tp ln no trc cng c, t nhn h s ra % mong mun,
    • Lu : cn chia sao tha mn
      • Tp train ln m hnh thng tin hc
      • Tp test ln m hnh d bo pha sau
      • Tp cal ln m hnh Mapie Clf hc cch d bo Pred Set
    • Tm thi, khuyn co t l v d nh: Train/Cal/Test ~ 60/15/25
  • GHI NH RNG: "CN CHIA THM 1 TP CAL (CALIBRATION) SAU NY DNG CHO MAPIE CLF"

    X_temp, y_temp, 
    test_size=0.2,       # Ly tp train/cal = 60%/15% 
    random_state=42, 
    stratify=y_temp
)

In[81]:
from sklearn.metrics import accuracy_score, f1_score, precision_score, recall_score
# Khi to danh sch lu kt qu
results = []
for name, model in fitted_models.items():
    y_test_pred = model.predict(X_test) 
    
    acc = accuracy_score(y_test_enc, y_test_pred)
    prec = precision_score(y_test_enc, y_test_pred, average='weighted', zero_division=0)
    rec = recall_score(y_test_enc, y_test_pred, average='weighted')  
    f1 = f1_score(y_test_enc, y_test_pred, average='weighted')
    
    results.append({
        "Model": name,
        "Accuracy": round(acc, 4),
        "Precision": round(prec, 4),
        "Recall": round(rec, 4),
        "F1_weighted": round(f1, 4)
    })

# To bng kt qu
results_df = pd.DataFrame(results).sort_values(by="F1_weighted", ascending=False).reset_index(drop=True)
results_df

2.3: LU V CHNH XC CA M HNH (QUAN TRNG)

  • BN CHT KT QU D ON C BN
    • Bn cht m hnh phn loi khi d bo .predict thng X_test bt k, s lun tr v "xc sut m n c th c xp vo tng nhm" (y_proba) PROBCLASS nh trong bng di
    • Sau t ng ct threshold thu c nhn d bo y_pred cui cng
    • Cui cng so snh nhn d bo y_pred vi nhn tht y_test thu c bng metric F1 v confusion matrix m ta vn thng thy nh trn

    • Vy th nhng thng X/y d bo b sai th sao? R rng l khi trin khai thc t th ta khng th bit c, khng h c nhn y_true ta kim tra
    • Ta phi chp nhn rng d l m hnh hay con ngi lun lun c sai s, ch t c 9x % chnh xc
  • VN NY SINH
    • Vy nu khch hng/i tc yu cu tr v cc h s nghi ng xem xt duyt th ta tr v nh th no? M hnh ng tin n mc no h khng bit c
    • V d nh c nhng thng X m m hnh d bo ra class0 60%, class1 40% tc l m hnh ang phn vn gia 2 class ny

    • Vy th ch cn setting thm phn ct ngng, nu max(y_proba)< 75% th tr h s v chng hn? Nhng cch ny kh l ch quan, khng n cht no
  • GII QUYT
    • Ta s dng 1 model ph l MAPIE CLASSIFICATION, (ct ngng linh hot) d bo ra PREDICTION SET - tp nhn d bo - cho nhng thng X m m hnh phn vn, t tr nhng thng X ny v cho khch hng/i tc xem xt
  • GHI NH RNG: "CHNG TA TRAIN MODEL LI CHN RA MODEL TT NHT, KIM TRA TIN CY CA N BNG MAPIE CLF"

3. MAPIE CLF UNDERSTANDING

3.0: THNG TIN CHI TIT

  • LINK ENG
    • https://mapie.readthedocs.io/en/latest/examples_classification/4-tutorials/plot_main-tutorial-classification.html
    • https://mapie.readthedocs.io/en/latest/generated/mapie.classification.MapieClassifier.html
  • THUT TON
    • "C th c lt qua":
    • Sau khi train model li tt nht trn (XGBoost chng hn)
    • Ta fit MapieClassifier ln tp X/y_cal. Tc gi s khng i su vo thut ton ca hp en, tng l:
      • Mapie dng chnh li hun luyn t X/y_train (xgb_model) d bo cho X_cal
      • Mi thng X_cal thu c y_proba_cal
      • Tnh sai s gia y_proba_cal vi y_cal
      • Thu c nonconformity l phn phi sai s (sai s gia "xc sut d on" so vi "nhn tht")
      • Ly tng t tin cy, ly Q l phn v 95% ca phn phi ny
      • Cng tr Q vo 2 pha ca y_proba_test to khong xc sut upper lower cho y_proba_test
      • Ct ngng linh hot thu c PREDICTION SET cho tng thng X_cal
  • THUT TON NGN GN
    • Fit Mapie bng tp Cal
    • Output c Prediction set (tp nhn d bo) cho tng X_test
  • GHI NH RNG: "MODEL LI FIT BNG TP TRAIN => MAPIE CLF FIT BNG TP CAL => PREDICT SET CHO TP TEST"

3.1: FIT MAPIE CLF

  • CC SETTING HIN TI
    • estimator: dng model c ch s tt nht cht Phn 2 (xgb_model)
    • cv & score: gii thch rt di, hi chatgpt hoc c link ti liu bn trn. Tm thi khuyn co c dng setting ph thng nht nh trong code

3.2: PREDICTION SET

# THAY I ALPHA TI Y  HIU C KT QU PRED SET S THAY I NH NO KHI ALPHA THAY I
# HIN TI ANG DNG  TIN CY 0.99 = 99%  TRC QUAN CC TRNG HP CHO ANH EM XEM
alpha = 0.01

# 1. D on t m hnh MAPIE
y_pred_mapie, y_pset = mapie_clf.predict(X_test, alpha=alpha)

df_result["Prediction Set"] = [
    set(np.where(row == 1)[0]) 
    for row in y_pset
]

    lambda s: {int(x) for x in s}

  • KT QU TRC QUAN
    • Nhn vo ct Prediction Set:
      • Mu xanh: Pred Set tr v 1 nhn duy nht v n ng chnh xc nhn tht y_test
      • Mu vng: Pred Set tr v 2 nhn tr ln v n "cha" ng y_test trong .
      • Mu : Pred Set tr v mt hay nhiu nhn no nhng khng h cha y_test tc l d bo sai hon ton.
    • ngha:
      • Mu xanh: m hnh d bo 1 nhn v "trng phc"
      • Mu vng: m hnh d bo nhiu nhn v chc chn rng nhn tht nm trong (m hnh phn vn, tr v cho ngi xem xt)
      • Mu : thc t ta khng h bit l nhng dng ny nm u khi trin khai, y ch n gin l sai s phi chp nhn, d m hnh tr v 1 hay nhiu nhn th vn c th c nhng trng hp l nhn tht khng h nm trong Set
  • IM MU CHT
    • Mapie gip ta tr v nhng dng mu vng con ngi xem xt thay v d bo 1 nhn v chp nhn sai s
    • Chuyn ha "sai s chp nhn" (mu alpha = 0.01) thnh "ri ro pht hin" / "h s xem xt" (mu vng alpha = 0.001)
    • Khi tin cy tng th m hnh s phi to ra thm nhiu Pred Set cha t 2 nhn tr ln trnh sai s
  • S NH I
    • Thc cht m hnh li xgb ban u (khi cha Mapie) chnh l tr v Pred set ch cha 1 nhn y_pred, v ch t mu xanh & cho bng ny
    • Mapie da vo tin cy gip cho m hnh tr v nhng thng phn vn, gim sai s chp nhn mu
    • Vy l ta chp nhn thm nhiu dng b tr v xem xt gim sai s chp nhn
    • Tuy nhin iu ny lm cho nhiu dng ng ra l "trng phc" ri (mu xanh alpha = 0.01) li b tr thnh "h s xem xt" (mu vng alpha = 0.001)
  • CU HI V CHNH SCH
    • Vy th nn Setting alpha & tin cy nh no m hnh cn bng gia vic tr v d bo v vic gim sai s chp nhn
    • Ta tm bng cch: ti mi alpha, ta tnh
      • bao ph - coverage
      • S nhn tr v trung bnh - width
    • Nh trong on code di y
In[87]:
from mapie.metrics import classification_coverage_score, classification_mean_width_score

# 1. To alpha grid
alpha_grid = np.arange(0.005, 1, 0.005)

# 2. D on prediction set cho ton b alpha
_, y_ps_all = mapie_clf.predict(X_test, alpha=alpha_grid)

# 3. Tnh coverage v width cho mi alpha
coverages = [
    classification_coverage_score(y_test_enc, y_ps_all[:, :, i])
    for i in range(len(alpha_grid))
]
widths = [
    classification_mean_width_score(y_ps_all[:, :, i])
    for i in range(len(alpha_grid))
]

# 4. To bng kt qu
df_alpha_analysis = pd.DataFrame({
    "alpha": alpha_grid,
    "Coverage": coverages,
    "Avg_Set_Width": widths
})

display(df_alpha_analysis.head(10).style.format({
    "alpha": "{:.3f}",
    "Coverage": "{:.4f}",
    "Avg_Set_Width": "{:.2f}"
}))

  • COVERAGE - BAO PH
    • Ti 1 dng bt k, Pred Set cha y_test th tr v True, ri tnh True/All
    • Cng nhiu dng c Pred Set cha y_test th Coverage cng cao
    • Ni d hiu, y l " chnh xc trong vic bao ph: d bo ra c tp nhn c cha nhn tht"
  • WIDTH - S NHN D BO TRUNG BNH
    • Tnh trung bnh ca Set Size
    • Cng nhiu dng c Set Size > 1 th Width cng tng
    • Ni d hiu, y l "s nhn c tr v trung bnh"
  • GII THCH NGHA BNG
    • Ti mi alpha, ta thy coverage xp x tin cy (1-alpha)
      • y l iu t nhin v Mapie dng chnh tng t tin cy to hp en
      • Khi ta chy lnh .preditct (alph=...) th chnh l mapie dng ng phn v 1-alpha ca phn phi sai s (nonconformity) to ra khong sai s bao ph (Q)
      • Tm li, v mt l thuyt th coverage s xp x tin cy lun, y chnh l % s dng mu xanh
    • Ti alpha 0.035
      • Width = 1, tc l trung bnh Set size = 1, tc l trung bnh mi dng m hnh ch d bo 1 nhn cho Pred set
      • y chnh l trng hp li xgb ban u, vi chnh xc l 96,6% dng mu xanh, cn li l mu , "gn nh khng c li mu vng"
      • Thc ra l c nhng rt him, cc him dng mu vng, bn cht vn chnh l li xgb ban u
    • Khi gim alpha, tng tin cy
      • Cng tng tin cy/ chnh xc th m hnh cng phi m rng sai s bao ph, khin tng nhiu Pred set 2 nhn, tc tng s h s tr v
      • Coverage cng gn 100% (khng bao gi t c), th m hnh cng s sai, cng tr v nhiu Pred set 2 nhn, thm ch 3-4 nhn

  • TH COVERAGE & WIDTH THEO TIN CY
    • Khi fit mapie, c th ngi thc hnh s nhm u , ta cn in ra th coverage v width kim tra
    • L tng vi hu ht ci bi:
      • Coverage xp x, trng vi ng tin cy 1-alpha theo l thuyt
      • Width c on cui b vnh ln tng mnh, y chnh l hin tng tr v qu nhiu nhn do mong mun tin cy tim cn ln 100% nu trn
  • V VON D HIU
    • Mun ng bc s a khoa on ng bnh cho 1000 bnh nhn, v s sai nn ng ta on mi ngi 1 n 3 bnh ri tr kt qu cho bc s chuyn mn xem xt tip.
    • Nhng tr v qu nhiu th qu phin phc, ng bc s a khoa ny v dng khng gip c g (m hnh ML - quy trnh AI khng t ng ha c, khng khc g b phn thm nh th cng ban u)
    • Vy nh no l bc s a khoa gii?
    • L vi mi bnh nhn, ng bc s ch on 1 bnh v trng phc lun, chnh xc n 96.6%. Chp nhn sai s 3.4%
    • Hoc cn bng c gia "s h s c tr v" v "sai s chp nhn"
  • THNG TIN PH
    • Ti sao c nhng dng m Width < 1?
    • y l nhng trng hp ni lng qu, tin cy thp; m hnh thu hp khong upper lower, khng d on nhn no c
    • Tr v set rng (), set size = 0
    • Tuy nhin, ti liu ny cha cp ti phn tnh th cng hp en nn tm hiu rng:
    • y l nhng trng hp "vt i", khng cn quan tm
    • Ch cn quan tm nhng alpha & tin cy ny c Width >= 1

3.3: KT LUN NGN GN D HIU

  • M HNH MAPIE KIM TRA TIN CY CA M HNH XGB LI V KHNG NH RNG:
    • "Nu mun h thng t ng ha hon ton (ch tr v 1 nhn) th m hnh m bo tin cy/ bao ph/ chnh xc ln n 96% cc trng hp"
    • "Hy cn nhc gia tin cy mong mun v s lng h s phi tr v xt duyt, m hnh s tr v mt cch linh hot nhng thng m m hnh phn vn/khng chc chn"
    • "V d: Nu mun tin cy 99%, m hnh s in ra c Pred Set bao gm 92% trng hp ch tr v ng 1 nhn; 8% trng hp tr h s gm 2 nhn xem xt. V trong 100% ny c th c 1% sai s no u khng bit c m ta phi chp nhn"
  • PIPELINE CODE
    • Notebook trnh by trc quan hiu tng ch khng hng dn code
    • Ch cn nh cc bc chnh + ChatGPT/Claude/etcetc :"3
      • Chia 3 tp train/cal/test
      • Train li
      • Test ch s nh mi khi, chn best model lm li
      • Mapie kim tra tin cy ca best model
        • Cal fit mapie
        • Setting alpha n
        • In ra df gm Predset v Proba v y test kim tra
        • Th nghim thay alpha xem output thay i nh no
        • Setting alpha grid
        • In ra df gm Coverage v Width ti mi alpha
